  <brief_title>Preference Tiotropium Respimat Study in COPD</brief_title>
  <official_title>Cross-sectional Study to Assess the Handling , Patient Satisfaction, and Preference for Inhalation Devices in Patients With Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD).</official_title>
  <sponsors>
